<c.white><c.mono_sans>My muscles won't work anymore!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1079
00:37:33.710 --> 00:37:34.753 position:46.19%,start align:start size:17.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Odo?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1080
00:37:36.796 --> 00:37:37.839 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well, say something.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1081
