1106
00:38:39.985 --> 00:38:43.529 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You might as well accept the</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1107
00:38:43.571 --> 00:38:44.948 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's what I'm going to do.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1108
00:38:45.031 --> 00:38:48.076 position:34.76%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm just going to</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1109
00:38:45.031 --> 00:38:48.076 position:34.76%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>lie here and die!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1110
00:38:48.118 --> 00:38:49.327 position:38.57%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>( grunting )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1111
00:38:59.254 --> 00:39:01.464 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>My brother will get the bar.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1112
00:39:02.174 --> 00:39:07.304 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:79.29% 
