1183
00:41:48.131 --> 00:41:50.383 position:38.57%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>( groaning )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1184
00:41:58.433 --> 00:42:00.185 position:44.29%,start align:start size:21.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Quark!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1185
00:42:07.233 --> 00:42:08.734 position:44.29%,start align:start size:21.43% line:84.62% 
