00:42:27.504 --> 00:42:30.340 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You'll find his body</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1192
00:42:27.504 --> 00:42:30.340 position:30.95%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
