1193
00:42:30.923 --> 00:42:34.844 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No doubt he'd want to vacuum</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1194
00:42:30.923 --> 00:42:34.844 position:30.95%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>desiccate his remains</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1195
00:42:35.261 --> 00:42:36.762 position:30.95%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
