00:43:07.793 --> 00:43:08.878 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Bashir to Infirmary.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1206
00:43:09.254 --> 00:43:10.922 position:27.14%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
