1230
00:43:53.590 --> 00:43:58.094 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I actually made it</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1231
00:43:58.428 --> 00:44:00.012 position:40.48%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Astounded.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

